| **express**       | `npm install express`           | The **core web framework** for Node.js; handles routing, requests, and responses.                               | ‚úÖ Yes                   |
| **sequelize**     | `npm install sequelize`         | A **promise-based ORM** for Node.js that simplifies database interaction with SQL databases.                    | ‚ùå No                    |
| **mysql2**        | `npm install mysql2`            | MySQL client library used by Sequelize to connect and execute SQL queries.                                      | ‚ùå No                    |
