| **bcrypt**        | `npm install bcrypt`            | Used for **hashing passwords** securely before storing them in a database.                                      | ‚ùå No                    |
| **cookie-parser** | `npm install cookie-parser`     | Express middleware that **parses cookies** attached to HTTP requests.                                           | ‚úÖ Yes                   |
| **cors**          | `npm install cors`              | Middleware that **enables Cross-Origin Resource Sharing**, allowing APIs to be accessed from different domains. | ‚úÖ Yes                   |
| **jsonwebtoken**  | `npm install jsonwebtoken`      | Used to **generate and verify JWTs** for user authentication and secure communication.                          | ‚ùå No                    |
