| **nodemailer**    | `npm install nodemailer`        | Enables sending **emails directly from your Node.js app** (for verification, password resets, etc.).            | ‚ùå No                    |
| **socket.io**     | `npm install socket.io`         | Enables **real-time, bidirectional communication** between client and server (e.g., chat apps).                 | ‚ùå No                    |
| **uuid**          | `npm install uuid`              | Generates **unique identifiers** (useful for IDs, tokens, filenames).                                           | ‚ùå No                    |
